<L>__{exterior bus stop (day) med. long shot}
<A>__{the bus pulls up to a stop, the door opens, and the passengers begin to file out. the mckennas, together with louis bernard, are the last off the bus. arab helpers have already climbed to the roof of the bus, to unload the baggage. the clean cut airline baggage of the mckennas is in sharp contrast to the hessianroped bundles of the arabs. there are nearby fiacres to take the people to their various destinations in the city, and some small, undersized taxi cabs.}
